## Config for the pdf reader zathura

## Key mappings (for Colemak)
map e scroll down
map u scroll up
map n scroll left
map i scroll right

map E scroll half_down
map U scroll half_up

map <PageUp> navigate previous
map <PageDown> navigate next

map q quit
map Z quit

set browser xdg-open %s
set scroll_wrap false
set show_inputbar false

## COLORS
set default_bgcolor #002b36
set inputbar_bgcolor #002b36
set inputbar_fgcolor #839496
set statusbar_bgcolor #073642
set statusbar_fgcolor #93a1a1
set notification_e_bgcolor #dc322f
set notification_e_fgcolor #002b36
set notification_w_bgcolor #b58900
set notification_w_fgcolor #002b36
set completion_bgcolor #073642
set completion_fgcolor #93a1a1
set completion_hl_bgcolor #859900
set completion_hl_fgcolor #002b36

# customize pdf colors with CTRL-i
set recolor_lightcolor #002b36
set recolor_darkcolor #839496
